- "spent" refers to the total amount calculated by multiplying the call duration with the corresponding call price;
- "2023" is the specific year for which the data is being analyzed;
- "more than $100" is the threshold for filtering customers.

- "vocal captains" refers to customers with significant call durations;
- "sailed the seas of communication" refers to the total call duration;
- "most seasoned navigators" refers to customers with a total call duration greater than 5 hours.

